Maxima glanced at Aerotaur as he entered.

Then turned back to Perceptor, "She did well. Though in due time, she will be 
far better." She would not ener the CR for the time being. 

Her attention then went to Hydras. Her concern welled within her as she tried 
her best to hide it. Emotions or compassion was not something Decepticons or 
Predacons would show.. even if it were for a comrade. But... Hydras was 
partial Megatron.. & she swore eternal loyalty to Megatron.. let alone felt a 
bond to him. There was so much more to this concern that she just wanted it 
to stay hidden from the others. 

"Do what you can for him, Perceptor." Watching the immobile figure of Hydras. 

--part1_11f.21239a5b.2be092d4_boundary
